| :----------------------------------------------- | :-------- |
|                                                  | SC | GA |
| [Patrick Lipton Robinson](/Patrick_Lipton_Robinson) | 15 | 185 |

Source: \[11\] \[12\]

With [Susana Ruiz Cerutti](/Susana_Ruiz_Cerutti)'s candidacy no longer in play, the ninth meeting saw [Patrick Lipton Robinson](/Patrick_Lipton_Robinson) receive overwhelming support in both the [Security Council](/Security_Council) (15 votes) and the [General Assembly](/United_Nations_General_Assembly) (185 votes). Thus, with a final, almost anticlimactic vote, [Patrick Lipton Robinson](/Patrick_Lipton_Robinson) was officially elected for the last vacant seat at the Court, bringing the 2014 International Court of Justice election to its long-awaited conclusion.